# 规则名称,匹配逻辑,推荐用法
# HOST: 精确域名匹配。
# HOST-SUFFIX,尾部包含,最推荐，覆盖范围广且准确。
# HOST-KEYWORD,中间包含,用于拦截广告或特定厂商流量。
# HOST-WILDCARD: 通配符匹配。 作用：使用 * 或 ? 进行模糊匹配，灵活性极高。 例子：HOST-WILDCARD, *google*.com, Proxy
# USER-AGENT,软件特征,针对特定 App 的一键分流。
# IP-CIDR / IP6-CIDR: 无类别域间路由（IPv4/IPv6 地址段）。处理无法识别域名的底层流量。

# 例子
# HOST,apps.apple.com,zy
# HOST-SUFFIX,apple.com,zy
# HOST-KEYWORD,testflight,zy
# HOST-WILDCARD,imac.*,zy
# USER-AGENT,*FindMyiPhone?,zy
# IP-CIDR,139.178.128.0/18,zy

# NAME: Bybit Optimized
# AUTHOR: U0hZiY
# UPDATED: 2025-09-05
# DESC: Optimized Bybit rules with latest domains

# Specific domains
HOST,monitor-frontend-collector.a.bybit-aws.com
HOST,api3.bybit.biz
HOST,www.bybits.org

# Main domain suffixes
HOST-SUFFIX,bybit.com
HOST-SUFFIX,bybit.biz
HOST-SUFFIX,bybdc6.com
HOST-SUFFIX,byabcde.com
HOST-SUFFIX,byapps.net
HOST-SUFFIX,byd3c3.com

# Additional Bybit related domains
HOST-SUFFIX,bybit.cloud
HOST-SUFFIX,bybit.global
HOST-SUFFIX,bybit.co.kr
HOST-SUFFIX,bybit.com.br
HOST-SUFFIX,bybitapi.com
HOST-SUFFIX,bybit.net
HOST-SUFFIX,bybits.org

# Third-party services used by Bybit
HOST-SUFFIX,appsflyersdk.com
HOST-SUFFIX,geetest.com

# User-Agent rules for mobile app
# USER-AGENT,*Bybit*
# USER-AGENT,Bybit*

# Process rules for mobile app (backup)
# PROCESS-NAME,com.bybit.app
# PROCESS-NAME,com.bybit.global